Interface TUMOnlineRequestFetchListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivityForAccessingTumOnline, ActivityForSearchingTumOnline, CalendarActivity, ChatRoomsSearchActivity, GradesActivity, LecturesAppointmentsActivity, LecturesDetailsActivity, LecturesPersonalActivity, OrganisationActivity, OrganisationDetailsActivity, PersonsDetailsActivity, PersonsSearchActivity, TuitionFeesActivity, WizNavCheckTokenActivity

    public interface TUMOnlineRequestFetchListener
    this interface should frame, how to implement a listener for the fetchInteractive method in TUMOnlineRequest

        void onFetchCancelled()

        void onFetchError(java.lang.String errorReason)

        Parameters:
        errorReason - the reason why the request failed (localized)
